data.description:
Welcome to this charming 5-bedroom ranch featuring over 2800 sq ft finished space. Enjoy the airy ambiance with 9' ceilings on Main and Lower level. 
Interior Highlights:
• 14’ Entrance ceiling on Main Level
• Quartz counters & maple cabinets throughout
• Spacious dining/sunroom opening to the deck.
• Fireplace Stone to Ceiling at Main Level Living Area.
• Popular LVP flooring enhances the open areas.
• Large Mudroom with Locker.
• Tile Bathrooms & Hvy Frameless Shower Door at MBR.
Lower Level Retreat:
• Huge family room wt a 2nd fireplace and a sit-at bar.
• 4th & 5th bedrooms and a full bath.
• Walkout basement, Abundant daylight through basement windows and Doors.
Exterior Features:
• LP Smart siding and stone detailing.
• 8 zone Lawn Irrigation with Wifi Assessable
• Four Wired eufy Cameras
Extra:
• Comes with brand new Washer, Dryer, Refrigerators in Kitchen & Bar.   
• Whole House humidifier System
• Composite Sink with Glass Riser
• Belt Driven Garage Door Opener and Car Charger
Great Location!! Don't miss the chance to own this modern, well-equipped home. Schedule your showing today! All infomation obtained from Seller and public records.
